### ========================================
### CART FLOW - Anonymous Checkout
### ========================================

### 1. Create New Cart (Get Session ID)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart

###

### 2. Get Cart by Session ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/cart/{{sessionId}}

###

### 3. Add Item to Cart
POST http://localhost:5000/api/cart/{{sessionId}}/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "{{productId}}",
  "size": "L",
  "color": "أسود",
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### 4. Update Cart Item Quantity
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/cart/{{sessionId}}/items/{{itemId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

###

### 5. Remove Item from Cart
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/cart/{{sessionId}}/items/{{itemId}}

###

### 6. Clear Cart
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/cart/{{sessionId}}

###

### ========================================
### ORDERS - Anonymous Checkout
### ========================================

### 1. Create Order (Checkout with Customer Info)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "{{sessionId}}",
  "firstName": "أحمد",
  "lastName": "محمد",
  "email": "ahmed@example.com",
  "phone": "01234567890",
  "streetAddress": "15 شارع الجامعة، الدقي",
  "city": "الجيزة",
  "state": "الجيزة",
  "notes": "من فضلك اتصل قبل التوصيل",
  "shippingFee": 50
}

###

### 2. Get All Orders (Admin)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders

###

### 3. Get Orders by Status
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders?status=pending

###

### 4. Search Orders by Email
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders/search?email=ahmed@example.com

###

### 5. Search Orders by Phone
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders/search?phone=01234567890

###

### 6. Get Order by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/orders/{{orderId}}

###

### 7. Update Order Status (Admin)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed"
}

###

### 8. Cancel Order
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/orders/{{orderId}}/cancel

